data.description:
Welcome to your own private oasis in the heart of tranquility! This stunning 1-story home with a refreshing pool & new roof invites you to embrace the epitome of luxury living. Nestled on a generously sized lot with no HOA restrictions, this residence offers the freedom to live your dream lifestyle.As you step into the foyer, you're greeted by an immediate sense of warmth and elegance, setting the tone for the entire home. The open-concept design seamlessly blends the living spaces, creating an inviting flow that's perfect for both daily living and entertaining. The heart of this home is the beautifully appointed kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space. Cooking enthusiasts will relish in the opportunity to prepare gourmet meals, all while enjoying views of the lush backyard through the large windows.

The spacious living room boasts an abundance of natural light, with French doors that provide easy access to the outdoor patio, where you can sip your morning coffee or host al fresco gatherings with friends and family. Enjoy the serenity of your own fenced backyard, complete with a sparkling pool that beckons you to take a refreshing dip on warm summer days.

Retreat to the three generously sized bedrooms, each offering its own en-suite bathroom. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, featuring a spa-like bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanities. The plush carpeting in the bedrooms adds a cozy touch, while the tile flooring throughout the rest of the home offers both style and practicality.

With an attached garage for your convenience, this home combines elegance with functionality. Whether you're relaxing by the pool, enjoying a quiet evening on the patio, or simply taking in the beauty of your private retreat, this residence offers a unique and luxurious lifestyle that's second to none.

Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a home that checks all the boxes - from the serene poolside escape to the no HOA freedom and stylish interior, this property truly has it all. Schedule your private tour today and make this dream home yours!

It's located just minutes to the Turnpike, I-95, Wellington, Boynton Beach, Downtown West Palm Beach, gorgeous area beaches and 3 international airports.
